{ The most logical response from White, 10. Nf3, does not work very well due to ...c6 ! We would challenge the center, making room for our pieces and, also, we will follow with the thematic ...e5 ! }
10... c6 11. a5 N6d7 12. e5
{ Black is not comfortable here due to White's space advantage and central domination. }
*

