7... Nxd5 8. Qxd5 { Other moves are clearly worse. } 8... Bxc3+ 9. bxc3 Qxc3+
10. Ke2 Qxa1 11. Be5 Qc1 { Black can force a draw if desired after } 12. Bxh8
Be6 13. Qxb7 Qc2+
{ Wherever the king goes, there will always be a check, be it on f5 or on c1/c2. }
