7... Nxd5 8. Qxd5 { Other moves are clearly worse. } 8... Bxc3+ 9. bxc3 Qxc3+
10. Ke2 Qxa1 11. Be5 Qb1 { Black wants to win ! } 12. Bxh8 Be6 13. Qd3 Qxa2+
