14. Bxc3 Bxc3 15. bxc3 Ne4 16. Rd4 Nxc3
{ gives White a very uncomfortable initiative after } 17. Qb2 Ne4 18. Bd3 Nc5
19. Bxf5 gxf5 20. Nh4 { White has a decisive advantage. } *

