8... Bg4 9. O-O-O Nd7
{ Once again, our knight wants to go to b6 and annoy the White's queen. } 10.
d5
{ As in most of the lines in the Russian System, we are happy with White giving us the e5 square, which we take by winning a tempo on the queen and generating some dynamic play with ideas like undermining White's center. }
