11. Qa3 { Playing prophylactically. } 11... b6
{ This is my main recommendation. Our idea is to continue with ...Bb7 and ...e5. }
12. e5 { White prevents us from playing e5. } 12... Bb7 13. h4 b5 14. h5 cxd4
{ 14... e6 was played in Twardon-Jasnikowski, Katowice op  (1993)  . However, Black needs to generate some kind of counterplay, which is why I recommend this novelty and the sequence that comes next. }
